StoredProcedureOraclev10g.name: INSERTCAMPUS
StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.INSERTCAMPUS(pName IN VARCHAR2, pLocation IN VARCHAR2, pAddress IN VARCHAR2,&lt;br/&gt;pPhone IN NUMBER, pFax IN NUMBER, pHead IN VARCHAR2) AS&lt;br/&gt;BEGIN&lt;br/&gt; INSERT INTO Campus_table &lt;br/&gt; VALUES(Campus_obj(seqCampus.Nextval, pName, pLocation, pAddress, pPhone, pFax, pHead));&lt;br/&gt; COMMIT;&lt;br/&gt;END insertCampus;
